And then let me start to I did prerecord this, but it is live.

00:07:40.820 --> 00:07:47.799
So let me start importing my Python libraries, setting up a connection.

00:07:47.799 --> 00:07:52.799
In this case, I'm connecting to a local in memory database, because that's the easiest

