00:15:06.359 --> 00:15:10.760
On the left here is the file explorer, and what you might notice if you have 20-20 vision

00:15:10.760 --> 00:15:15.880
is that I have downloaded these parquet files to this remote machine, right?

00:15:15.880 --> 00:15:17.760
So it's in a folder called data.

00:15:17.760 --> 00:15:21.200
And that's great, again, because like I mentioned, it's good if you're not talking over the Internet

00:15:21.200 --> 00:15:23.919
and you have local access to these data parquet files.

00:15:23.919 --> 00:15:27.159
So here's all my months of parquet files.

00:15:27.159 --> 00:15:29.520
