The two things that I've changed about this script for this demo is that, number one,

00:15:33.799 --> 00:15:39.719
I'm reading the parquet files from local folder called data instead of from the cloud.

00:15:39.719 --> 00:15:44.919
And then the second thing I did was I commented out the first filter that filters the dataset

